                    Pago M贸vil
                  </h3>
                  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-white">
                    <div
                      class="group cursor-pointer"
                      data-action="copy"
                      data-text="04121234567"
                    >
                      <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-1">Tel茅fono</p>
